overview: Every morning on Couleur 3, Vincent Kucholl and Vincent Veillon parody the news using swiss stereotypes.  On stage we meet again with those stereotypes: Sébastien Jacquet the junkie from la Riponne, Gilles Surchat recently fired from Schaffter Pives SA, Stève Berclas singer of BlackLion Genocide from Valais and lieutenant-colonel of the swiss army Karl-Heinz Inäbnit.
title: 120'' présente: La Suisse
